title: Spiced Chicken Strips & Creamy Sauce with Mash Potato & Garlic Veggies
description: The star of tonight's meal is this homestyle sauce; velvety sour cream is gently infused with Nan's special seasoning to make a sauce that pairs perfectly with chicken and fluffy potato mash. You simply won’t believe you made this amazing meal at home!

